            ,</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17891209-12-verdict67" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17891209-12-verdict67" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>, <rs id="t17891209-12-punish68" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17891209-12-punish68" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17891209-12-defend158 t17891209-12-punish68"></join>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17891209-12-defend160 t17891209-12-punish68"></join>
               Death
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury before Mr. Baron PERRYN.</p>
